                            <comment id="14806" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Wed, 28 Sep 2005 04:40:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for pointing this out, Erwin! I&apos;ve synchronized all MessageFormat format calls on the given MessageFormat instance. Synchronization shouldn&apos;t hurt too much there, as MessageFormats are only used for messages with arguments anyway: Resolution of messages with a  plain code circumvents the use of MessageFormat in the first place.&lt;/p&gt;

